{"tid":626812,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)群屍玩過界 鬼玩人2-3 無聲絕境","createTime":"2018-04-12T12:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T18:01:11.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cc708f6d242707ee33dfbd5b83e13d3d75f1f869","tid":626812,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:15:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=%2BI%2BMj8jsIKeOGRJVcOuxUviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=5fb7ba26\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=%2BI%2BMj8jsIKeOGRJVcOuxUviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=c988f7bf\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/9b/%E6%96%B0%E7%A9%BA%E6%88%BF%E7%A6%81%E5%9C%B0%E6%B5%B7%E6%8A%A5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9b%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E6%2588%25BF%25E7%25A6%2581%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%258A%25A5.jpg&h=bc987824&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/9a/The_Evil_Dead_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9a%2FThe_Evil_Dead_.jpg&h=4d52b72d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/f/fa/Army_of_Darkness.jpg/220px-Army_of_Darkness.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2Ff%2Ffa%2FArmy_of_Darkness.jpg%2F220px-Army_of_Darkness.jpg&h=43599523&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/345678_5797499895a2161e35aab9-1050x629.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F345678_5797499895a2161e35aab9-1050x629.jpg&h=bc79e697&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.幾名偷獵者在印度尼西亞的蘇門答臘島捕獲變異鼠猴，將其販賣給紐西蘭一家動物園。而在這家動物園所在的城市，一位受到母親過分管制的年輕人萊昂內爾&middot;科斯格羅夫與一位雜貨店女店員巴吉塔&middot;瑪麗亞&middot;桑切斯墜入愛河，但卻遭到其母親的反對。一次兩個年輕人在動物園偷偷約會，萊昂內爾的母親為了監視兩人的一舉一動而跟蹤兩人，卻一不小心被鼠猴咬到。本以為這只是皮肉之傷，卻不知凡是被咬到的人都會屍變成活死人，而且被活死人咬到的人同樣也會變為其同類。為了隱瞞這件事萊昂內爾把殭屍都藏在房子養了起來<br />\n<br />\n2安旭與妮塔前往郊外旅遊時，暫居在一處無人居住的空屋。當晚，他們在空屋內發現到一本「死亡之書」及一臺錄音機。但是，好奇的他們卻不小心誤將空屋內招喚惡靈的錄音帶播放出咒語，使得「死亡之書」的封印解開，令樹林間的惡靈甦醒過來。<br />\n由於，妮塔被惡靈附身後，欲向安旭痛下殺手，但未成功反遭受殺害。此時，傷心又無奈的安旭，惟有將妮塔埋葬，但惡靈仍控制她的屍體，輾轉進入他的身體之內。然而，隨後到達的兩對情侶卻突然來到此屋，並捲入其中&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n3.故事劇情描寫接續上部作品結尾，但卻在恐怖當中增加不少喜劇效果。整個舞台不在荒郊野外的空屋內拍攝，轉而移往中世紀的城堡裏，並添增許多人物及鬼怪角色，塑造出相似史詩般的大場面<br />\n<br />\n4.一群無堅不摧的攻擊性生物將地球佔領，並以聲音來捕獵 就算只是微弱聲響，都可能招致襲擊喪命。一個已失去一個孩子的倖存家庭，每日唯一保命的戒條就是 :「絕不能發出任何聲響!」，否則，父母和剩下的兩個小孩，還有即將出生的嬰兒，將面對前所未見的未知後果&hellip;靠靜默來續命，到底能橕多久?<br />\n<br />\n8 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=%2BI%2BMj8jsIKeOGRJVcOuxUviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=ba66f72a\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=%2BI%2BMj8jsIKeOGRJVcOuxUviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=0c5f8d97\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b320fb1cb8ecf2b25e90ecae6e8f9ce885f67a1f","tid":626812,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:16:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54959fca19a7d6ee007c4e8a5611ad97fc0e575c","tid":626812,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:30:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"920dec663e22fa575ab084876ae6be346ec4d52a","tid":626812,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32140b3867fb4e7ce6d7ba6d206425b55e0c7f7b","tid":626812,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1bab3cbf49f1e656cec6e93d12fa1d0e2523bbe","tid":626812,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:58:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b145d64dcd1e2d8cc8674f6d3bd356b9fae177","tid":626812,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e1d1eb03e7ce988f7b